        <h2 class="title">Hastauttanasana</h2>
        <p class="copy">Breath in and lift your arms up and back.
          Make sure that your biceps are close to your ears.
          Make effort to stretch your whole body starting from the heels up to the finger tips.</p>
        <a href="/practiceYoga/3">
